settings.description: Mario Adventures Through the clouds to get to Bowsers Castle, nowhere near yet...
HOW ARE YOU DOING THIS LAST JUMP RIGHT BEFORE THE FLAG OMG IT'S SO HARD I'M STUCK HERE!!!!!!
After a "long" adventure, you finally made it! Now you must go through the entire world to get to the final boss, bowser. Take the Hammer suit with you and a few more powerups to defeat him!
Roto-discs are like Fire Bars, but with much more room to dodge! Just make sure to keep your wits about you; they're a lot faster, too!
You find yourself in an unknown dimension, and you must find your ship. Will you escape, or will you stay here forever?
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.

Welcome to the Museum! Come gawk at some of the strange critters that are native to the Mushroom Kingdom!
Difficulty: 1/5
